Atlantean Nomad
A True Atlantean who wanders the megaverse trading, exploring, and fighting
the forces of the Splugorth. One of the most versatile dimension-walkers on
Rifts Earth, the Nomad combines magical tattoo power with broad survival skills.

Atlantean Nomads carry magical tattoos from birth. Their PPE pool fuels tattoo
activation. They are trained in dimensional navigation, multiple languages, and
lore of Rifts and magic. Skill picks come from Physical, Technical, Wilderness,
and Rogue categories.

Race restriction: Atlantean only.
Attribute requirements: None.
PPE: Starting pool (ppe_base + ME bonus) grows each level.
Starting equipment: Enchanted Atlantean armor, a short sword with at least one
magic tattoo weapon effect, dimensional compass, and survival gear.
